BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:OOYWSVWOkrYWH97Oc28n5
SUMMARY:Improvised Musical Style and Lyrics with Ron Hippe - Issaquah
DTSTAMP:20260410T044143Z
DTSTART:20260422T190000Z
DESCRIPTION:Find Your Voice\\\, Build Your Confidence\\\, and Create Songs 
	on the Spot!\\n\\n\\n\\nNow at Unexpected Productions’ new Issaquah locati
	on\\\, unlock your creativity in a supportive\\\, playful\\\, and joy-fill
	ed class designed for anyone who’s ever hummed in the car\\\, belted in th
	e shower\\\, or wondered\\\, “How do musical improvisers make that magic h
	appen?” \\nWhether you’re a seasoned improviser or stepping into musical i
	mprov for the first time\\\, this course welcomes you with open arms—no pr
	ior singing experience required. \\nWhat You’ll Learn\\nThis intensive\\\,
	 dynamic class explores the foundational skills of musical improvisation t
	hrough hands-on practice and group collaboration. You’ll learn how to: \\n
	\\nCreate songs and stories in the moment\\nUnderstand classic song forms 
	and how they apply to improv\\nStrengthen your sense of timing\\\, rhythm\
	\\, and rhyme\\nTurn simple prompts into memorable choruses\\nBuild lyrics
	 that feel poetic\\\, emotional\\\, or downright hilarious\\nJump confiden
	tly between styles—from Broadway to jazz\\\, pop to chants\\n\\nIt’s fun\\
